{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/InfiniteDungeon.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>The catacombs are dark and rife with the stench of undeath. What manner of foes linger beneath the city, no one can say, but it can be suffered no longer. Train, gear up, and gather your party to journey below the graveyard city of Tombsteel. Steel yourselves, resurface, resupply, and strategize before braving the depths again.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/DynamicCombat.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Journeyman offers the familiar tactical, party-based combat of traditional CRPGs and tabletop RPGs while adapting the Souls-like ARPG feel. Instead of pausing and planning, each party member must rely on each other in Realtime. Gone are the days of THAC0 and auto-attacks.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Combat.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/OnlineCo-op.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Forget behing a <i>henchman</i>. Journeyman was designed for the ground up for co-op. Embark on quests by yourself or with friends, in scenarios designed for both configurations.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Fellowship.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/DiverseClasses.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Play as a Warrior, Rogue, Wizard, Paladin, Ranger, or Bard. Each class may choose to specialize or remain a generalist based on your party's unique needs. Pick from a vast assortment of familiar talents, situational tools, and lifesaving utilities, ensuring no two playstyles are alike. Rely on your allies for support as you hurl magic fireballs from afar or charge headfirst into the front lines.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/ImmersiveWorld.png?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/BoundlessCustomization.png?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/QuestsAndRumors.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>No one is <i>handing out</i> quests. Prove yourself to the local lords, or keep an ear out for rumors after buying the local tavern-goers a few rounds. Will you side with the forces of justice or watch the world burn?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Dialogue.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/ArenasAndBattlegrounds.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Hone your skills against fellow champions, testing out new build configurations. Journeyman features a mid-match progression system where you earn gold from kills to buy and sell gear to gain the upper hand.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1723188706","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/page.bg.jpg?t=1723188706","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1723188706","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1723188706","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>FOLLOW DEVELOPMENT ON DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/InfiniteDungeon.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>The catacombs are dark and rife with the stench of undeath. What manner of foes linger beneath the city, no one can say, but it can be suffered no longer. Train, gear up, and gather your party to journey below the graveyard city of Tombsteel. Steel yourselves, resurface, resupply, and strategize before braving the depths again.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/DynamicCombat.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Journeyman offers the familiar tactical, party-based combat of traditional CRPGs and tabletop RPGs while adapting the Souls-like ARPG feel. Instead of pausing and planning, each party member must rely on each other in Realtime. Gone are the days of THAC0 and auto-attacks.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Combat.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/OnlineCo-op.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Forget behing a <i>henchman</i>. Journeyman was designed for the ground up for co-op. Embark on quests by yourself or with friends, in scenarios designed for both configurations.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Fellowship.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/DiverseClasses.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Play as a Warrior, Rogue, Wizard, Paladin, Ranger, or Bard. Each class may choose to specialize or remain a generalist based on your party's unique needs. Pick from a vast assortment of familiar talents, situational tools, and lifesaving utilities, ensuring no two playstyles are alike. Rely on your allies for support as you hurl magic fireballs from afar or charge headfirst into the front lines.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/ImmersiveWorld.png?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/BoundlessCustomization.png?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/QuestsAndRumors.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>No one is <i>handing out</i> quests. Prove yourself to the local lords, or keep an ear out for rumors after buying the local tavern-goers a few rounds. Will you side with the forces of justice or watch the world burn?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/Dialogue.gif?t=1723188706\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/extras/ArenasAndBattlegrounds.png?t=1723188706\" /><br>Hone your skills against fellow champions, testing out new build configurations. Journeyman features a mid-match progression system where you earn gold from kills to buy and sell gear to gain the upper hand.","developers":["Refactor Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2131360/header.jpg?t=1723188706","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256952156,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.